data.description: This charming home is situated on a peaceful cul-de-sac in North Pole, Alaska. The property boasts four spacious bedrooms, providing ample space for a growing family or hosting guests. The two updated bathrooms feature modern amenities and add to the home.  Notice the fresh and inviting atmosphere created by the new flooring and paint throughout the entire house.  One of the highlights of this property is its large backyard, providing a perfect outdoor space for various activities and gatherings. The deck coming off of the kitchen enhances the outdoor experience, offering a great spot for relaxation or entertaining guests. Whether you want to enjoy a quiet morning coffee or host a barbecue with friends, the backyard and deck provide the ideal setting. Overall, this 4-bedroom home in North Pole, AK combines modern updates, a convenient layout, and a tranquil location, making it a desirable residence for those looking for comfort and style in the northern part of Alaska. Take a 3D tour here, https://my.matterport.com/show/?m=B4a7GJ9dTXG
